    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Finger of Death</strong> (Level 7 Necromancy)</p><p>You send negative energy coursing through a creature that you can see within range, causing it searing pain. The target must make a constitution saving throw. It takes 7d8 + 30 necrotic damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><p>A humanoid killed by this spell rises at the start of your next turn as a zombie that is permanently under your command, following your verbal orders to the best of its ability.</p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> 60 feet | <strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p><p><em>Classes: Sorcerer, Warlock, Wizard</em></p>",
